      • slideToLocation

        public boolean slideToLocation(MappedInLocation location)
        Method to make the Sliding panel slide to the requested location. If the location is found and the slide is successful then it will return true, otherwise false.
        Parameters:
        location - MappedIn location to make the panel slide to
        Returns:
        true if the sliding was successful, false otherwise.
